{
  "version": "1",
  "questId": "fr_08",
  "lang": "ru",
  "lines": [
    {
      "key": "000fc05",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Теплая шапка согреет голову.",
      "sourceEnText": "A warm hat keeps your head warm.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_000fc05.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1881,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:52Z",
      "textHash": "d7733bc9a66fb43b66098228b2496f3c1c04d9d467c4d3f87aa456b492194127"
    },
    {
      "key": "001e940",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Давайте ответим на три вопроса о горах перед игрой в флаг.",
      "sourceEnText": "Let's answer three mountain questions before the flag game.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_001e940.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2900,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:19Z",
      "textHash": "ea86ab36cdf5d227ed57c3a59aba16996eab3b0f69d0c5119bebfaaa1391762b"
    },
    {
      "key": "003e87c",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_bonus",
      "sourceText": "Ты нашла тёплый шарф!",
      "sourceEnText": "You found a warm scarf!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003e87c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1463,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:34Z",
      "textHash": "8670ba052ac498a0544e28e5fccfd0953f5126dee6b97f44413671fcb2202aab"
    },
    {
      "key": "003ecb2",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Монблан — самая высокая гора в Альпах!",
      "sourceEnText": "Mont Blanc is the highest mountain in the Alps!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_003ecb2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2142,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:36Z",
      "textHash": "313ef056152becb43d1235e45142390bd2fa8a4c28654a8349071fe67a69c696"
    },
    {
      "key": "00a7e83",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Правильно! Используйте их, чтобы сохранять устойчивость.",
      "sourceEnText": "Correct! Use them to stay steady.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_00a7e83.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3213,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:07Z",
      "textHash": "2414e11b3a7f635ecc338d0e7e7f6a9f78dca9468854c9429775a024dbe33d5d"
    },
    {
      "key": "011dc7e",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Я обожаю горы!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love the mountains!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_011dc7e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1176,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:35Z",
      "textHash": "f83e7705ec8c9dacfb037c5463153a09abf474a0ea52c88870c2ce829872a35c"
    },
    {
      "key": "015bf8a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Теперь вы готовы к восхождению!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are now ready to climb!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_015bf8a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1829,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:45Z",
      "textHash": "23ac36a23bb6473dbabd0ef25485364dbec152e1124cd50be3d92be38fdbfe6a"
    },
    {
      "key": "018880a",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Высота этой вершины составляет 4807 метров.",
      "sourceEnText": "This summit is 4807 meters high.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_018880a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3135,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:12Z",
      "textHash": "1e57cc6b0cea0bf2271b0b00a6fac5250e2dce2901bac3856b17047b82fe5d73"
    },
    {
      "key": "01a4b20",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Ласты",
      "sourceEnText": "Flippers",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01a4b20.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 705,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:07Z",
      "textHash": "8f3d57e76ad1ba687b618e5fef737a0534c72f224a148fb0b1c0efc9e81a9fef"
    },
    {
      "key": "01beb5e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Мы видели, как собака бежала вверх по горе.",
      "sourceEnText": "We saw the dog run up the mountain.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01beb5e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2351,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:39Z",
      "textHash": "60be811e15e559dc43001e292050c06ad0542ee6b297cbda0856ee412383e34d"
    },
    {
      "key": "01e5f66",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Этот ледник выглядит как замерзшая река.",
      "sourceEnText": "That glacier looks like a frozen river.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_01e5f66.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2377,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:41Z",
      "textHash": "16e88013f76c61c1c4c0079aed177743040c607d7b005d003a6826320eaa55d3"
    },
    {
      "key": "029a03e",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Солнце на снегу светит очень ярко. Нам необходима защита для глаз.",
      "sourceEnText": "The sun on the snow is very bright. We need eye protection.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029a03e.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4023,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:56Z",
      "textHash": "40347702389efffda1d71ca571e34781afe0ce694f85f6cb77052aeabbab090f"
    },
    {
      "key": "029f39c",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "Теперь мы можем покинуть базовый лагерь и начать приключение!",
      "sourceEnText": "Now we can exit the base camp and start the adventure!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_029f39c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3265,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:45Z",
      "textHash": "1c2000ac9e6eef02879f3618fe2957189eda7cd45c8883b2aa20c690e22df76d"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a2ea9",
      "nodeTitle": "item_sunglasses",
      "sourceText": "Снег и лед отражают яркий солнечный свет.",
      "sourceEnText": "Snow and ice reflect bright sunlight.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a2ea9.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2534,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:01Z",
      "textHash": "40e599f2520a4ca9f583517afd013d9b551728c184a73e783a87a5e18bb3f7a0"
    },
    {
      "key": "02a3874",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Нет, я остаюсь здесь.",
      "sourceEnText": "No, I stay here",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02a3874.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1411,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:31Z",
      "textHash": "2edc69ba3c2cdc3783846b591c8d20704396434b9655b104e91ae3a8ed8b175c"
    },
    {
      "key": "02c9805",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_3_done",
      "sourceText": "Откройте сундук, чтобы достать кошки!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get crampons!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_02c9805.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:09Z",
      "textHash": "0116f349462939e82850e716b180e94d24cb6d97d6faa21ac2ba4e83e99b92c7"
    },
    {
      "key": "030fa1c",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base4",
      "sourceText": "Вы добрались! Мы на вершине Монблана.",
      "sourceEnText": "You made it! We are at the top of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_030fa1c.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2142,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:11Z",
      "textHash": "75d2202ba6d669f538d459f81a79eab186686c06e6723228f1aaf6952de38366"
    },
    {
      "key": "035e68a",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовый лагерь 4",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 4",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_035e68a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1228,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:30Z",
      "textHash": "3b4e61185d6718f6f796409cb35c4b2e7909732edcf79f7a0e18cba754640af8"
    },
    {
      "key": "0371d31",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "Восхождение с гидом безопаснее.",
      "sourceEnText": "Climbing with a guide is safer.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0371d31.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1829,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:44Z",
      "textHash": "d8c16995ac1c369ca9e4f4a25d20815d0889f9ba5f4d44594a70dd8dec8f1d0a"
    },
    {
      "key": "038d1bc",
      "nodeTitle": "item_rope",
      "sourceText": "Веревка помогает альпинистам оставаться в безопасности на льду и скалах.",
      "sourceEnText": "The rope helps climbers stay safe on ice and rock.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_038d1bc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3971,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:11Z",
      "textHash": "1b23f1ed86f4458e27757a19a68fa69c34624ff0bbbe631594a711f9f94d0231"
    },
    {
      "key": "03db010",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_swiss",
      "sourceText": "Швейцария расположена к северу от Монблана.",
      "sourceEnText": "Switzerland is north of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03db010.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2534,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:21Z",
      "textHash": "0eeeec9baef0e1b2e0eeda9e1c5c856372b2f95e299bc4089c0611f26730d73e"
    },
    {
      "key": "03dd802",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Пальто отсутствует!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the coat!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_03dd802.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1280,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:47Z",
      "textHash": "b65e327d29a7d37ec9fc69871a665e92f660ada2f5e8d1d57fe0712daffbabdb"
    },
    {
      "key": "045409f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Перед поездкой вам понадобится рюкзак.",
      "sourceEnText": "Before going, you need a backpack.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_045409f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2011,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:41Z",
      "textHash": "91c4ce037c46322b953930e06e6687b0e222376cba437a314aef8f2e9f42e1c1"
    },
    {
      "key": "046eb33",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Вернитесь, когда закончите задание.",
      "sourceEnText": "Come back when you finish the task.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_046eb33.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2142,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:38Z",
      "textHash": "9097e173b4cef480dbcb6b14916966db2add4768fc5c859c111898f882cf64e4"
    },
    {
      "key": "04bbada",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Надеюсь увидеть сурка!",
      "sourceEnText": "I hope to see a marmot!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04bbada.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1463,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:37Z",
      "textHash": "3577340f9eac5139e720ff1d8460b2fb5401c888c52180c3dd0f6c98b192cfb4"
    },
    {
      "key": "04c1c1f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Я вижу, у тебя есть рюкзак. Теперь можешь идти!",
      "sourceEnText": "I see you have the backpack. Now you can go!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_04c1c1f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2717,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:35Z",
      "textHash": "477a1d875753529b0afa282cda7b9b4ee5186f3739ea68cf055b46181ae228fe"
    },
    {
      "key": "050fe70",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_italy",
      "sourceText": "Италия расположена к востоку от Монблана.",
      "sourceEnText": "Italy is east of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_050fe70.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2429,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:20Z",
      "textHash": "8edbd1404db1cfaf106ed1d2cab978962e442acb5f23f8d65b6836ad7c726016"
    },
    {
      "key": "0557ef5",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Ветер может быстро меняться.",
      "sourceEnText": "The wind can change fast.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0557ef5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 1541,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:40Z",
      "textHash": "614e9d95b90455889fbbd3bfa6d7076e0111e3e1dfe4c22091bf75f89f660c99"
    },
    {
      "key": "056ec2b",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_base1",
      "sourceText": "Открывается! Внутри находится некоторое оборудование.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It contains some equipment.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_056ec2b.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3265,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:50Z",
      "textHash": "017963d53bffea8d9a746683851e825fb28754b7f43c8570d6cfe8b47933c069"
    },
    {
      "key": "058bb65",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовый лагерь 3",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 3",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_058bb65.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1176,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:29Z",
      "textHash": "30279bdee46e5093ea5795983a2efc4cdb5ece8c5cecbc0514b31616a55fbec3"
    },
    {
      "key": "0590129",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Не забудьте взять теплую одежду!",
      "sourceEnText": "Don't forget to bring warm clothes!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0590129.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1776,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:38Z",
      "textHash": "75f782630dec0e8aac44ce560313386f8f53213f55a6cee6f3ffd00bdfef7664"
    },
    {
      "key": "059d744",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Это также помогает, когда дует холодный ветер.",
      "sourceEnText": "It also helps when the wind is cold.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_059d744.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2482,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:52Z",
      "textHash": "28d2f739a1ef69d6d51672a41ec77296eefcf08b78d54f354236836c0e4517b3"
    },
    {
      "key": "05cabb5",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Поищите вокруг!",
      "sourceEnText": "Look around for it!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05cabb5.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1123,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:42Z",
      "textHash": "fedd714eb9c4547c09bab90c166e5a5b69ba5bb7b070fafa8a82842d0255b16d"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e3658",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовый лагерь 2",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 2",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e3658.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1123,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:29Z",
      "textHash": "086b3c976e1f18d0afe0345b4c40ebadc650d5bb142d2e8602f6295794f25275"
    },
    {
      "key": "05e80cb",
      "nodeTitle": "item_backpack",
      "sourceText": "В этот рюкзак можно положить еду, воду и карту.",
      "sourceEnText": "This backpack can carry food, water, and a map.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_05e80cb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2795,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:44Z",
      "textHash": "c711dacb4f42ff4ddc55c43bf451fd4762699360019a8a8eb268b67888aee36f"
    },
    {
      "key": "0650acc",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Пожалуйста, исследуйте Монблан и найдите наше снаряжение.",
      "sourceEnText": "Please explore Mont Blanc and find our gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0650acc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3318,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:40Z",
      "textHash": "ee9fee51d6823c53b717017390a138233e432e759632d0c7f473edf9956e2224"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b15bb",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "У вас есть ледовое снаряжение. Последний рывок к вершине!",
      "sourceEnText": "You have the ice gear. One last push to the top!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b15bb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3396,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:03Z",
      "textHash": "30132e59a3b2a89a3e95b2ceac6e49c56de2102f7d5cbfd444a4e6b26a94d02f"
    },
    {
      "key": "06b3363",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Перчаток не хватает!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the gloves!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06b3363.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1306,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:55Z",
      "textHash": "492a7b1dccdb0005988058257d8bdcc51425a1b00f3e1d2a83cbb254457c9f15"
    },
    {
      "key": "06d9f34",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Для ходьбы по ледниковому льду нам необходимо специальное снаряжение.",
      "sourceEnText": "To walk on glacier ice, we need special gear.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06d9f34.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3605,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:04Z",
      "textHash": "440ffb2a713cf774603f271bdbe26628a3f81dd0527510ea3c37ab2311f75b67"
    },
    {
      "key": "06f9a2a",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "В каком горном хребте находится Монблан?",
      "sourceEnText": "What mountain range is Mont Blanc in?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_06f9a2a.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2299,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:14Z",
      "textHash": "24ee60fbb6d84da2aa185885cc232de356536d059088d44609fcbc78bbd81993"
    },
    {
      "key": "07102e7",
      "nodeTitle": "item_crampons",
      "sourceText": "Они помогут вам безопасно ходить по льду.",
      "sourceEnText": "These help you walk safely on ice.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07102e7.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2299,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:10Z",
      "textHash": "8ef9186ad5d51bb6b48b3506823c5b841bc6e0c7c690a70d8891dd9177a501b3"
    },
    {
      "key": "0724de3",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Помогите! Я горный гид. Синяя собака украла наше альпинистское снаряжение!",
      "sourceEnText": "Help! I am a mountain guide. A blue dog took our climbing gear!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0724de3.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5172,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:39Z",
      "textHash": "428a3ea2b74e714b506244a7284d435b89a333c8a729312067f823c373c6a35e"
    },
    {
      "key": "076433f",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Что надевают на ботинки, чтобы ходить по льду и не поскользнуться?",
      "sourceEnText": "What do you put on your boots to walk on ice and not slip?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_076433f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3448,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:05Z",
      "textHash": "be395507f61299df3b1f1e8526234b1751302a35312d15bd3a9616d90c1d821c"
    },
    {
      "key": "07c6385",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Нет! Вы не плаваете! Попробуйте ещё раз.",
      "sourceEnText": "No! You aren't swimming! Try again.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07c6385.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2351,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:08Z",
      "textHash": "991b670fe8dabf28be7453532c113270708b922a1fa95689d8ac066320d1d7d4"
    },
    {
      "key": "07f2635",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Базовый лагерь 1",
      "sourceEnText": "Basecamp 1",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07f2635.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1306,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:28Z",
      "textHash": "e8f1bb13a8a49751d64d9f1e2c7356333f4d906895ba2e5b95644d871a8cd219"
    },
    {
      "key": "07f2699",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Найдите все альпинистское снаряжение и узнайте больше о трех соседних странах!",
      "sourceEnText": "Find all the climbing gear and learn about the three nearby countries!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_07f2699.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 4624,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:17Z",
      "textHash": "a5dee2364362b9240d022b5347f6161a6998cf2597976fd87a2e84d7224b68f6"
    },
    {
      "key": "0809dce",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "Я обожаю альпинизм в Альпах.",
      "sourceEnText": "I love climbing in the Alps.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0809dce.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 1724,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:42Z",
      "textHash": "61b6aa626c94c8cd7308dfa5dcea71419587fd9f8cd1b34dfdf501fbc6206ab2"
    },
    {
      "key": "081fbe4",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_alps_climber",
      "sourceText": "Кошки помогают мне ходить по твердому льду.",
      "sourceEnText": "Crampons help me walk on hard ice.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_081fbe4.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2429,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:43Z",
      "textHash": "4a2048314d455820931e8cc3e14acfcbed8e2a7991d289397f0da0b67d214fc1"
    },
    {
      "key": "088fb7f",
      "nodeTitle": "item_sunglasses",
      "sourceText": "Солнцезащитные очки защищают ваши глаза.",
      "sourceEnText": "Sunglasses protect your eyes.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_088fb7f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2482,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:02Z",
      "textHash": "fb087ac9757eb94219b628abc2a100b2aa7b6ea784244067ba2ad733be0996f2"
    },
    {
      "key": "097ecf0",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_tourist",
      "sourceText": "Горы могут быть опасны, поэтому будьте осторожны!",
      "sourceEnText": "Mountains can be dangerous, so be careful!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_097ecf0.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_F",
      "durationMs": 2560,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:22Z",
      "textHash": "c416ee373c5a36dd3ca49fe977d42dfa26f368af11eb0404978f885908e87334"
    },
    {
      "key": "0a70f7d",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Что защищает глаза от яркого снега и солнца?",
      "sourceEnText": "What protects your eyes from bright snow and sun?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0a70f7d.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2560,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:18Z",
      "textHash": "f17dae9e828641ad99889f9b3d344138f8190ec8a22474ad7e1c4857578da2ce"
    },
    {
      "key": "0a7146f",
      "nodeTitle": "item_hat",
      "sourceText": "Теперь вы можете продолжить восхождение!",
      "sourceEnText": "Now you can continue the climb!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0a7146f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:53Z",
      "textHash": "5acf54631ccf6c3ef6bfd3a2289f47010c328c170bffb10b84d2bdda0301bbe4"
    },
    {
      "key": "0afb2dc",
      "nodeTitle": "item_scarf",
      "sourceText": "Шарф защищает шею от ветра.",
      "sourceEnText": "A scarf blocks wind on your neck.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0afb2dc.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1881,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:35Z",
      "textHash": "07f3067a3de47f43175280f2207c8a4d1ab112258a259c101be2b3febdb9fc91"
    },
    {
      "key": "0b50050",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Кошки",
      "sourceEnText": "Crampons",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0b50050.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 679,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:06Z",
      "textHash": "eb24f0053d5c23bb96af6df12a72c3416e0adba94b666936023f618df5d16853"
    },
    {
      "key": "0bc67f7",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Когда на льду, я иду вдоль веревочной линии.",
      "sourceEnText": "I follow the rope line when it is icy.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0bc67f7.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2482,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:41Z",
      "textHash": "0a90f8f1e282d5f27e304393d8225430c8a00c23514f8f8903df048cb3f328c7"
    },
    {
      "key": "0c18060",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Вам нужна помощь, чтобы подняться на гору?",
      "sourceEnText": "Do you need help to climb the mountain?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0c18060.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2247,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:27Z",
      "textHash": "daed94ec4d7c502b35210492764a2833aa32d6fd648c4a9da165174c61bd1b42"
    },
    {
      "key": "0c18c08",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base3",
      "sourceText": "Вам не хватает веревки!",
      "sourceEnText": "You are missing the rope!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0c18c08.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1358,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:03Z",
      "textHash": "978a890dc9f0d5072d72e55751efa8bbf489609f987801da0bc85ada2733f53b"
    },
    {
      "key": "0c1f006",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_intro",
      "sourceText": "Открывается! Внутри рюкзак.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It contains a backpack.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0c1f006.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1724,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:42Z",
      "textHash": "ccc0712f65348c658e91d5da46c052d284188f0bde023f1b9b906952c00f42da"
    },
    {
      "key": "0d01879",
      "nodeTitle": "item_gloves",
      "sourceText": "Холодные руки затрудняют восхождение.",
      "sourceEnText": "Cold hands make climbing hard.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0d01879.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2299,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:00Z",
      "textHash": "f30ae47df28d5ee8c86301285c418cbac4c07cce9e8f9626848ab6709ccc9026"
    },
    {
      "key": "0d23529",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_france",
      "sourceText": "Франция расположена к западу от Монблана.",
      "sourceEnText": "France is west of Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0d23529.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2299,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T16:42:20Z",
      "textHash": "615e7fb98a51a31a797e0763a29a2e7516fadbe4102bb4d465844cc128e32adc"
    },
    {
      "key": "0dbac73",
      "nodeTitle": "spawned_hiker",
      "sourceText": "Для пеших прогулок здесь необходима хорошая обувь.",
      "sourceEnText": "Hiking here needs good boots.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0dbac73.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "ADULT_M",
      "durationMs": 2795,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:39Z",
      "textHash": "108caadf521c0df8bd6f9d32ec88d52d33670cab1a5a0671f17297fb2a48e145"
    },
    {
      "key": "0e23f1f",
      "nodeTitle": "item_coat",
      "sourceText": "Это пальто согреет вас в ветреную и снежную погоду.",
      "sourceEnText": "This coat keeps you warm in wind and snow.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0e23f1f.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3318,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:51Z",
      "textHash": "524b94d0fc2315a829d8802cae1435cc9944c350b65195a57c564cad2aed7649"
    },
    {
      "key": "0e83480",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_1_done",
      "sourceText": "Откройте сундук, чтобы достать теплую шапку!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get a warm hat!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0e83480.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2664,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:49Z",
      "textHash": "670d617c4858be9baa0428a3799f00d19765adeac397f9f7a076782d580957a6"
    },
    {
      "key": "0f2aac7",
      "nodeTitle": "item_gloves",
      "sourceText": "Перчатки сохраняют пальцы в тепле и сухости.",
      "sourceEnText": "Gloves keep fingers warm and dry.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0f2aac7.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2534,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:00Z",
      "textHash": "869945fbbb6c6cb440eca96494e611a63b8119fb3af4fc8ed62c1af3b1296aad"
    },
    {
      "key": "0f4644b",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_intro",
      "sourceText": "Давайте поднимемся на Монблан.",
      "sourceEnText": "Let's climb Mont Blanc.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0f4644b.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1698,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:36Z",
      "textHash": "1459e02d826f2c3ae658e5e16874c2f134f73e9966d8cfb0e1d7b633f0ed34b4"
    },
    {
      "key": "0f4c405",
      "nodeTitle": "snowman",
      "sourceText": "Да",
      "sourceEnText": "Yes",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0f4c405.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 522,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:27Z",
      "textHash": "bd178ddd4fa220c8b73738441937cc0df39b31ade16780dade5f460e80d0ee72"
    },
    {
      "key": "0fdc3cb",
      "nodeTitle": "activity_2_done",
      "sourceText": "Откройте сундук, чтобы достать солнцезащитные очки!",
      "sourceEnText": "Open the chest to get sunglasses!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_0fdc3cb.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2900,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:58Z",
      "textHash": "6d2a4670781d1c301ed048413a2bbb11ab11337e3a822233e9229acd84a147b9"
    },
    {
      "key": "b1_1",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Начинает дуть ветер. Моим ушам нужна защита!",
      "sourceEnText": "The wind is starting to blow. My ears need protection!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_b1_1.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2978,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:48Z",
      "textHash": "16b6dfaca0653dfbb12b28a0653b7f1e265d24b66e2801b8d52752e495398f66"
    },
    {
      "key": "b1_q",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base1",
      "sourceText": "Как защитить уши при сильном ветре?",
      "sourceEnText": "How do we protect the ears when the wind is strong?",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_b1_q.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2116,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:48Z",
      "textHash": "bc99f17dad6d898b0d8450dbd4b38fb3878c21e30f5039903ab993f1c12d824d"
    },
    {
      "key": "chest_locked",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_intro",
      "sourceText": "Оно заперто. Возможно, вам нужен ключ.",
      "sourceEnText": "It's locked. Maybe you need a key.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_chest_locked.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2299,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:43Z",
      "textHash": "738824589094d6f2a506048c09086329217fc897338845e31300624f833d7577"
    },
    {
      "key": "comebacklater",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "Заходите позже!",
      "sourceEnText": "Come back later!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_comebacklater.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 1176,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T18:59:05Z",
      "textHash": "1bc4343e92aa443ce16fbcfb66c92deeae8247b0acbf8d2d5a9018863b86918b"
    },
    {
      "key": "correct",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "Правильный!",
      "sourceEnText": "Correct!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_correct.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 888,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:15Z",
      "textHash": "d1923208935c5fde39fc5542db67fd313c1f03c6c511d07de08f286f93638826"
    },
    {
      "key": "dontknow",
      "nodeTitle": "question_alps",
      "sourceText": "Я не знаю",
      "sourceEnText": "I don't know",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_dontknow.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 705,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T18:59:04Z",
      "textHash": "2d0c1a993a6f85eda690f986c1cfdebe642a888b73eda299e557d4674947b23c"
    },
    {
      "key": "end_1",
      "nodeTitle": "quest_end",
      "sourceText": "Удивительно! Вы достигли вершины Монблана. Его высота составляет 4807 метров!",
      "sourceEnText": "Amazing! You reached the top of Mont Blanc. It is 4807 meters high!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_end_1.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 5486,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:33Z",
      "textHash": "84fa862db024ce0394b360030cb07a73215400068a6239241bf294005da5b589"
    },
    {
      "key": "end_2",
      "nodeTitle": "quest_end",
      "sourceText": "Альпы полны высоких, прекрасных гор.",
      "sourceEnText": "The Alps are full of tall, beautiful mountains.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_end_2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2247,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:34Z",
      "textHash": "80206ba13ddde5513134b677926d523b69911e28b61c82cbd75a418d4535ebb2"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_b2_chest",
      "nodeTitle": "chest_base2",
      "sourceText": "Оно открывается! Внутри находятся солнцезащитные очки.",
      "sourceEnText": "It opens! It has sunglasses inside.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_b2_chest.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3553,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:59Z",
      "textHash": "7f04a36cc8223b58dc4b81338a2064c76fc9bd8b7c0fc8a9bac50871a0fafb80"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_b2_help",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
      "sourceText": "Если вы застрянете, снеговик вам поможет!",
      "sourceEnText": "If you get stuck, the snowman can help!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_b2_help.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2247,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:39:54Z",
      "textHash": "4f3864ddb763899baa44c5ad8c542c0ffb54ca55d348dfa38b03e76680062032"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_2",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "Всю зиму я сплю под снегом. Это называется спячка!",
      "sourceEnText": "I sleep all winter under the snow. This is called hibernation!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_2.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 2795,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:32Z",
      "textHash": "c7a74e6f986402cf28c67ed63d0a916eb8cc5b62a9c0fab69190a0583fb79545"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_3",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "Я обожаю есть альпийские цветы и траву. Объедение!",
      "sourceEnText": "I love eating alpine flowers and grass. Yum!",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_3.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3265,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:32Z",
      "textHash": "aeaa468389be8b7a4bc7aa96db89122dc5b661662e0d5b4b13720591396bd8e2"
    },
    {
      "key": "fr08_marmot_4",
      "nodeTitle": "marmot",
      "sourceText": "Не обращайте на меня внимания, я просто загораю на этом тёплом камне.",
      "sourceEnText": "Don't mind me, I'm just sunbathing on this warm rock.",
      "audioFile": "fr_08_fr08_marmot_4.mp3",
      "voiceProfile": "felix",
      "actorId": "Default",
      "durationMs": 3500,
      "updatedAt": "2026-03-15T12:40:33Z",
      "textHash": "80b2bcf42f4094f6ca56279eaff03b33195fbd72980301288bf3a4bb78a48eed"
    },
    {
      "key": "keep_looking",
      "nodeTitle": "npc_base2",
